Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens Christus auf dem Stroh Maria und Kind Johannes. Antwerpen Augsburg" addressed to "Herrn Prof. Dr. H. G. Evers 6101 Traisa / Darmstadt Waldstr. 43" and dated 16.01.1970

- Correspondence with Franz Huber dated 1968
- Message dated 1966 with a photocopy of a reproduction of the 'Virgin and the Child' by Rubens attached
- Descriptions and notes about the 'Virgin and the Child' by Rubens

  
Loose documentation in the Rubensdocumentation of the Rubenianum:   
    
- 2 photos of Mary with the Child (Rubenianum "Evers 1993" stamp on the back)
